findings.title: Owner can set total buy, sell, and transfer fee up to 19% each
findings.description: The owner has the capability to set high fees (up to 19%) for buying, selling, and transferring, which could lead to unintended consequences or exploitation.

findings.title: State Variable Default Visibility
findings.description: Variables can be specified as being public, internal, or private. Explicitly define visibility for all state variables.

findings.title: A floating pragma is set (SWC-103)
findings.description: A floating pragma is set which can cause varying bytecode between builds.
